1. the size of the array is fixed, not able modify the size.

2. not able to store heterogeneous/dissimilar values.

3. no proper API is there for an arrays.

-------------------------------------------------------------------

The above problems we can Overcome with Java Collections

1. the size of the Java Collections is not fixed, able modify the size

2. able to store heterogeneous/dissimilar values.

3. we have proper API is there for Java Collections.